>>> import sys
>>> import locale
>>> sys.getdefaultencoding()
'ascii'
>>> locale.getdefaultlocale()
('ru_RU', 'UTF-8')

I think it is more correct to use UTF-8 everywhere or use locale.getdefaultlocale() instead sys.getdefaultencoding().
